parameters:
It seems impossible to pass without an umbrella, such a
half-hearted rain.

I was waiting for the rain to stop while absentmindedly
looking up at the cloudy sky.

In that moment, a flashy-dressed woman entered the
space.
Huh? Oh, there's someone else here before me.
Don't be disappointed when you see someone's face.
It was Kanae, who lives next door.

Well, I think I can recognize the faces of most of the kids
in the neighborhood.
Hey, weren't you not wearing glasses?

What~? Are you trying to show off for a cute girl or
something?
Kanae at that time was an incredibly talkative person,

The machine gun talk that shoots without interruption is
mostly an attack towards me and never ends.

Well, we used to play together when we were kids, but as we
got older, things became a bit awkward. So, I'm
honestly happy to have this long-awaited reunion.

She's always like the protagonist who is at the center of
everything, while I'm like a background character who
doesn't stand out no matter where I am.
Oh~ It's been a while! Have you been doing well?
I don't think I've seen you at all recently.
Are you properly attending classes and stuff?

There's absolutely no problem, in fact, I'm aiming for perfect
attendance.

Hehe, long time no see~ I haven't seen you in a strangely
long time.
As for me, well, I'm doing fine in my own way.
Except for being constantly told by my mother to study!

Even the other day, you know, I had my expensive mascara
that I bought with great determination stolen from me!
I think thats your own fault.
Geez! Even Hikaru is saying that!

After hearing complaints from Kanae about her parents like
that, Kanae lightly tapped her thigh as if her legs
were hurting and stretched.

After that, I saw some benches around and immediately tried
to sit down, so I placed a handkerchief on top and
underneath the bench.

I sat down next to her while casually ignoring the words
asking if I was trying to seduce her.
No matter how I think about it, it's different. Haha...

Do you know how many boys are trying their best to have a
conversation with the super beautiful Kanae-sama in one
go?
Kanae's face, which is approaching in an instant.

Kanae started sniffing around my neck while sniffing her
nose.

The glossy blonde hair, it's like a retriever, I couldn't
help but stroke it.

When I lowered my hand that was halfway up, Kanae was just
sniffing and smelling without thinking about anything.

Surprisingly mature. Are you the type who likes this
kind of thing?

But, you seem like a guy who doesn't know anything about
this kind of thing...
Oh my... not just the change in image, but also...
So, you've found someone you like, huh?
I just bought it after watching a TV show once.
But, it smells a little like girls' perfume.
You're using quite an expensive one, huh?
Ah, hey! What's with the sudden punch!
Kanae, snatching the perfume, sprayed it all over the place.
...As I thought, or rather, did I overdo it?
That's not how you're supposed to put it on.
Look. You don't need to put on so much perfume.
